1. Open VBox
2. Open terminal and enter into root user
3. install qemu-kvm
4. install libvirt-bin bridge-utils qemu-system virt-manager
5. nano /etc/libvirt/libvirtd.conf
6. uncomment listen_addr and save the file
7. change all to 0777
8. Restart the service
9. Install cirros image
10. Choose vm image
11. Run cirros image
12. Perform login
